In the heartbeat classification task, the region pooling block generates heartbeat feature maps for the predicted heartbeat regions [2]. Feature maps in the last four layers (with strides 8, 16, 32, 64) are reused to extract heartbeat features. Because these feature maps have different sizes, the predicted regions are mapped as: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
